      <title>收錄: Linux常用命令</title>
      <link href="/posts/jp-19539/"/>
      <url>/posts/jp-19539/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="I-Linux常用命令："><a href="#I-Linux常用命令：" class="headerlink" title="I.Linux常用命令："></a>I.Linux常用命令：</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd -     退到上一層目錄</span><br><span class="line">cd ..     退到上兩層目錄</span><br><span class="line">ls        查看當前路徑下的檔和資料夾</span><br><span class="line">ls -l     查看當前路徑下的檔和資料夾的詳細資訊（許可權）</span><br><span class="line">ls | grep &quot;sou&quot;  查看當前路徑下的名字包含“sou”的檔和資料夾</span><br><span class="line">mkdir dir1    創建目錄，名為“dir1”</span><br><span class="line">rm dir1       刪除名為”dir1“的檔</span><br><span class="line">rmdir dir1     刪除名為”dir1“的目錄   （目錄為空的情況）</span><br><span class="line">rm -rf dir1    刪除非空的名為&quot;dir1&quot; 的目錄</span><br><span class="line">cp file1 file2   把file1資料夾複製到file2資料夾中（file1為空資料夾的情況下）</span><br><span class="line">cp -r file1 file2   把file1資料夾複製到file2的資料夾中</span><br><span class="line">grep  &quot;關鍵字&quot;   /../../..路徑          在檔file1中查找關鍵字</span><br><span class="line">gedit  /../../..路徑       查看此路徑下的檔</span><br><span class="line">apt-get update      升級所有套裝軟體</span><br><span class="line">apt-get upgrade    升級已安裝的套裝軟體</span><br><span class="line">history   查看所有歷史命令</span><br><span class="line">history | grep &quot;svn co&quot;     查看包含有&quot;svn co&quot;關鍵字的歷史命令</span><br><span class="line">給檔修改所有為所有人可讀許可權：</span><br><span class="line">chmod a+r linuxyw.com</span><br><span class="line">給檔修改所有為所有人可執行許可權：</span><br><span class="line">chmod a+x linuxyw.com</span><br><span class="line">給檔修改所有為檔屬主用戶可執行許可權：</span><br><span class="line">chmod u+x linuxyw.com</span><br><span class="line">把linuxyw目錄下的檔設置為所有人可執行許可權：</span><br><span class="line">chmod -R a+x linuxyw/</span><br><span class="line">把linuxyw目錄下的檔全部設置為755許可權：</span><br><span class="line">chmod -R 755 linuxyw/</span><br><span class="line">取消linux目錄下的所有檔可寫許可權：</span><br><span class="line">chmod -R a-w  linuxyw/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="II-終端常用快捷方式"><a href="#II-終端常用快捷方式" class="headerlink" title="II.終端常用快捷方式"></a>II.終端常用快捷方式</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Shife + Ctrl + T     新建終端</span><br><span class="line">Shife + Ctrl + Q    關閉終端</span><br><span class="line">Shife + Ctrl + C   複製</span><br><span class="line">Shife + Ctrl + V   粘貼</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Shife + Ctrl + PageUp   頁面向上移一頁</span><br><span class="line">Shife + Ctrl + PageDown   頁面向下移一頁</span><br><span class="line">F11      全屏</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl + C    強行關閉運行的命令</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl + Z    切換到後臺運行</span><br><span class="line">fg      把切換到後臺運行的命令調出來</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="III-Linux下查看電腦硬體設定"><a href="#III-Linux下查看電腦硬體設定" class="headerlink" title="III.Linux下查看電腦硬體設定"></a>III.Linux下查看電腦硬體設定</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">系統: </span><br><span class="line">uname -a               # 查看內核/ 作業系統/CPU信息</span><br><span class="line">head -n 1 /etc/issue   # 查看 作業系統版本</span><br><span class="line">cat /proc/cpuinfo      # 查看CPU信息</span><br><span class="line">hostname               # 查看電腦名</span><br><span class="line">lspci -tv              # 列出所有PCI設備</span><br><span class="line">lsusb -tv              # 列出所有USB設備</span><br><span class="line">lsmod                  # 列出載入的內核模組</span><br><span class="line">env                    # 查看環境變數</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">資源:</span><br><span class="line">free -m                # 查看記憶體使用量和交換區使用量</span><br><span class="line">df -h                  # 查看各分區使用情況</span><br><span class="line">du -sh &lt;目錄名&gt;        # 查看指定目錄的大小</span><br><span class="line">grep MemTotal /proc/meminfo   # 查看記憶體總量</span><br><span class="line">grep MemFree /proc/meminfo    # 查看空閒記憶體量</span><br><span class="line">uptime                 # 查看系統執行時間、使用者數、負載</span><br><span class="line">cat /proc/loadavg      # 查看系統負載</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">磁片和分區:</span><br><span class="line">mount | column -t      # 查看掛接的分區狀態</span><br><span class="line">fdisk -l               # 查看所有分區</span><br><span class="line">swapon -s              # 查看所有交換分區</span><br><span class="line">hdparm -i /dev/hda     # 查看磁片參數(僅適用於IDE設備)</span><br><span class="line">dmesg | grep IDE       # 查看啟動時IDE設備檢測狀況</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">網路:</span><br><span class="line">ifconfig               # 查看所有網路介面的屬性</span><br><span class="line">iptables -L            # 查看防火牆設置</span><br><span class="line">route -n               # 查看路由表</span><br><span class="line">netstat -lntp          # 查看所有監聽埠</span><br><span class="line">netstat -antp          # 查看所有已經建立的連接</span><br><span class="line">netstat -s             # 查看網路統計資訊</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">進程:</span><br><span class="line">ps -ef                 # 查看所有進程</span><br><span class="line">top                    # 即時顯示進程狀態</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">用戶:</span><br><span class="line">w                      # 查看活動用戶</span><br><span class="line">id &lt;用戶名&gt;            # 查看指定使用者資訊</span><br><span class="line">last                   # 查看使用者登錄 日誌</span><br><span class="line">cut -d: -f1 /etc/passwd   # 查看系統所有使用者</span><br><span class="line">cut -d: -f1 /etc/group    # 查看系統所有組</span><br><span class="line">crontab -l             # 查看當前用戶的計畫任務</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">服務:</span><br><span class="line">chkconfig --list       # 列出所有系統服務</span><br><span class="line">chkconfig --list | grep on    # 列出所有啟動的系統服務</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">程式:</span><br><span class="line">rpm -qa                # 查看所有安裝的套裝軟體</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
